sage\" class=\"success-message\">\n        <p> Felicitats! Has mantingut premut el bot贸 el temps necessari! </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <b-button variant=\"primary\" href=\"/cognitiva\" class=\"next-button\">\n        Anar al seg眉ent exemple de Discapacitat Cognitiva\n      </b-button>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script>\nexport default {\n  name: \"Motriu2\",\n  data() {\n    return {\n      successMessage: false, // Missatge d'猫xit\n      holdTimeout: null, // Controla el temps que es mant茅 premut el bot贸\n    };\n  },\n  methods: {\n    startHold() {\n      this.holdTimeout = setTimeout(() => {\n        this.successMessage = true;\n        setTimeout(() => {\n          this.successMessage = false;\n        }, 3000); // El missatge desapareix despr茅s de 3 segons\n      }, 3000); // Temps necessari per activar el bot贸\n    },\n    endHold() {\n      clearTimeout(this.holdTimeout); // Es cancel路la si el bot贸 no es mant茅 premut el temps suficient\n    },\n    cancelHold() {\n      clearTimeout(this.holdTimeout); // Es cancel路la si el cursor surt del bot贸\n    },\n    navigateHome() {\n      window.location.href = \"/\"; // Navegar a l'inici\n    },\n  },\n};\n</script>\n\n<style>\n/* Contenidor principal */\n.motriu {\n  height: 100vh;\n  width: 100vw;\n  background-color: #f5f5f5;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 20px;\n}\n\n/* Contenidor central */\n.content-container {\n  text-align: center;\n  color: #333;\n  padding: 20px;\n  border: 2px solid #ccc;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n}\n\n/* Text explicatiu */\n.explanation {\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n  color: #444;\n}\n\n/* Contenidor del bot贸 */\n.hold-button-container {\n  margin: 20px 0;\n}\n\n/* Bot贸 que requereix ser mantingut */\n.hold-button {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  background-color: #ffc107;\n  color: white;\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  border-radius: 